Name: DESIGNATION OF TELEPHONE NUMBER
Explanation: USED TO IDENTIFY A SPECIFIC TELEPHONE NUMBER, I.E. THE DEUTSCHE BUNDESPOST (DBP).

Name: TELEPHONE NUMBER
Explanation: THE TELEPHONE NUMBER OF AN AGENCY OR ORGANIZATION.

Name: NON-SECURE TELEPHONE
Explanation: THE DESIGNATED NON-SECURE TELEPHONE NUMBER OF AN INDIVIDUAL OR AGENCY TO BE CONTACTED.

Name: SECURE TELEPHONE NUMBER
Explanation: THE DESIGNATED SECURE TELEPHONE NUMBER OF AN INDIVIDUAL OR AGENCY TO BE CONTACTED.

Name: NON-SECURE FACSIMILE (FAX) NUMBER
Explanation: THE TELEPHONE NUMBER OF A NON-SECURE (UNCLASSIFIED) FAX

Name: SECURE FACSIMILE (FAX) NUMBER
Explanation: THE TELEPHONE NUMBER OF A SECURE (CLASSIFIED) FAX.

Name: TELEPHONE NUMBER, INDIVIDUAL
Explanation: THE TELEPHONE NUMBER OF THE INDIVIDUAL.

Name: GATEWAY ACCESS PHONE NUMBER
Explanation: THE PHONE NUMBER TO GAIN ACCESS TO THE SADL GATEWAY.
